title: Bug 130068[Regression]Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when preview a report with parameter.
description: Description: Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
OB: When previewing a report with parameters, the Report Parameter window does not appear.
EB: When clicking on Preview in Layout, the Report Parameter window should pop up for value input.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open a report.
2. Click on Preview in Layout button.
